"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1897765-Team-GB-Noah-Williams-Olympic-Games\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Noah Williams wants to honour the memory of the coach who ignited his Olympic dreams by securing a medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 110, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999986889634, \"rank\": 1.311027496454781e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the memory\", \"from\": 30, \"to\": 40}, {\"ngram\": \"the coach\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic dreams\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The diver from Hackney finished 27th on his Olympic debut in Tokyo, missing out on a semi-final attempt, and later sent a message to his followers onInstagramwhich read: \\\"Thank you for all the support, I am sorry I could not do you proud x\\\".\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Hackney\", \"score\": 0.9999493981328889, \"rank\": 3.60358365697151e-05, \"text\": \"Hackney\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Hackney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Hackney\"}, {\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6303616751914425, \"rank\": 0.5862055015566463, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The diver\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 127}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic debut\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 175}, {\"ngram\": \"a semi-final attempt\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"his followers\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"all the support\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But performances in the pool were soon placed firmly into perspective after the death of his much-loved coach Dave Jenkins in October 2021.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\", \"score\": 0.9999986764809937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dave Jenkins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"performances\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"the death\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"his much-loved coach\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old's life was turned upside down and he considered retiring from the sport he loved.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 23-year-old's life\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of this (Olympic) cycle is done in his memory,\\\" Williams said.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"this (Olympic) cycle\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"his memory\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to quit after he passed.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard when someone passes who is your main motivator, he was training me for events.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"your main motivator\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really did not enjoy diving after that.\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It still would have been completely different if he just quit, diving would be different, but because he did pass away, it was a lot to process.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the first time in my life that I'd had anything like that to deal with.\\\"\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jenkins was a mentor and a friend to Williams, who had been his coach's prot\\u00e9g\\u00e9 since the age of 16 at London Aquatics Centre.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Aquatics_Centre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"London Aquatics Centre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Aquatics_Centre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Aquatics_Centre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jenkins\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"a mentor\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"a friend\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach's prot\\u00e9g\\u00e9\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after taking time to process the grief, a switch flicked and he was all of a sudden embarking on a second Olympic quest.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"the grief\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"a switch\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"a second Olympic quest\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I stuck through it and I ended up thinking the opposite, that I could not quit because I wanted to do something in his memory,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opposite\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"his memory\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not know what else to do apart from dive.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dive\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not leave it on Tokyo so hopefully I can do well in Paris for him.\\\"\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6303616751914425, \"rank\": 0.5862055015566463, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1